Smoking and vaping may be permitted only during authorized rest breaks or lunch breaks (no exceptions), and only in designated outdoor areas outside the view of patients or other guests who might be arriving or departing. If you smoke before work or during a rest break or lunch break, please take all reasonable steps to ensure that when you begin or resume work, the smell of tobacco is not on your person, your breath or your clothing. 
